events.text:
We are in dire need of wood here, the type of wood that is hard and dry, not the wet-like spongy wood most commonly found here.
There are caches of wood out in the forest that have been cured by time and dried like a raisin by the sun.
Go out and there wouldn't you retrieve this wood would ya?
Wouldn't you know? Have you found the caches of wood yet?

I know it was understood that you would gather wood while I stood here.
You did good, so it betooks me to honor your work in this murk.
Here ya go lad. best smithwork I've encountered in the land.
But before you jolt off in the distance...
